# Lorenzo's Barber Shop Website

WEDE5020 Part 3 Final POE Submission

Student: [Friend's Name]
Student Number: [Student Number]

This website was developed as part of the WEDE5020 Portfolio of Evidence (POE). The project demonstrates the implementation of HTML,
CSS, JavaScript, Search Engine Optimization (SEO), form validation, interactive gallery features, responsive design principles, and GitHub version control.

Version 3.0 – Final POE Submission (June 2026)

Added

* Search Engine Optimization (SEO) meta tags on all web pages.
* JavaScript form validation for booking forms.
* Interactive image gallery lightbox.
* Google Maps location section on the Find Us page.
* Automatic booking confirmation page with countdown redirect.
* Hover animations on navigation links and gallery images.
* Responsive page layout using CSS Grid.
* Mobile-friendly design improvements.

Improved

* Website folder structure organized into:
    * css/
    * js/
    * images/
    * documents/
* Navigation bar consistency across all pages.
* User experience through interactive elements.
* Image gallery presentation and accessibility.

Fixed

* Broken image paths.
* Navigation highlighting issues.
* Booking form validation errors.
* Gallery lightbox closing functionality.
* General HTML validation issues.

Technologies Used

* HTML5
* CSS3
* JavaScript
* GitHub
* Google Maps Embed API

